Ace Magashule eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Suspended ANC Secretary-General Ace Magashule is in hot water yet again. This time the ANC says it will investigate him over comments he made over the weekend. Magashule was heard calling on disbanded ANC structures to disobey the leadership. READ: WATCH | Magashule won't go down without a fight - analyst "What we are doing is trying to understand, we will ask him to explain himself," said deputy Secretary-General, Jessie Duarte, who was briefing the media on Tuesday. Duarte says there are no structures that are disbanded as it would be favour of certain individuals. She says this is an attempt to create discord among certain members of the party. Suspended ANC Secretary-General Ace Magashule is in hot water yet again. This time the ANC says it will investigate him over comments he made over the weekend. Magashule was heard calling on disbanded ANC structures to disobey the leadership. #eNCA #DStv403 pic.twitter.com/jk5upNVguD